  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the fact that he-- that Horthy got arrested and put into house arrest, and the fact that he issued immediately ordered the Jews had to wear a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was too many signs which brought back signals that it's going to be bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I started to look again somehow for a smuggler who would help me to get across to Romania.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I found one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I left Hungary in May of 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, I have to mention that before leaving Hungary, there was the so-called [NON-ENGLISH] which is now very well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Eichmann took two Jewish leaders, Zionist leaders and gave them a private plane, and sent them on his plane to Turkey to negotiate with [NON-ENGLISH] who was sort of like a foreign minister, Hungary's number two, to negotiate releasing Jews for trucks.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, while this story I won't get into that, because this is a long chapter which is what happened to them and so forth and so forth.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But many Jews like myself had those big hopes that heard Brand flew with the plane, he would come back, and we will allow somehow be released from Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I didn't believe in that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Many Jews did, including, I have an uncle, who was also in Hungary at that time, who came after I came.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Only because the same way he found out from earlier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told me I'm making a big mistake going to Romania because I'm risking myself, and this is almost sure that Eichmann is negotiating.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know Brand was sent to Turkey with a private plane?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And can you imagine that the Jews will not be willing to collect money to give Hitler a few of these lousy trucks so that-- to save Jews?",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
